@startuml Result Polling Flow

title Result Polling

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API Server" as API
database "Database" as DB

FE -> API : GET /executions/{id}
API -> DB : Query execution status
DB --> API : Execution record
API --> FE : { status, stdout, stderr, execution_time }
FE --> User : Display result

note right of FE
  Frontend polls until
  status is COMPLETED,
  FAILED, or TIMEOUT.
end note

@enduml
